----------------
Gestuftes Gel&#228;nde ca. 15m. Langer Hang exp. NE, Gratnah. Schneeh&#246;he 3.20m mittel.

PROFILE
-------
CT und ECT am RB. Gut verfestigte Schneedecke keine Schwachstellen

RUTSCHBLOCK
-----------
Keine Ausl&#246;sung m&#246;glich

SNOW SURFACE
------------
Vielf&#228;ltig, grossenteils glatt, Luvseiten abgefegt, Leeseitig D&#252;nen. Extreme Schattenlagen Oberfl&#228;chenreif.

SNOW DRIFT
----------
Kein neuer, alte Ablagerungen zugedeckt

ALARM SIGNS
-----------
Keine

AVALANCHES
----------
Keine neuen

AVALANCHE DANGER
----------------
Stufe 2 oberhalb 2000m. Kammlagen, Rinnen und Mulden. Unterhalb 2400m Gleitschneeabg&#228;nge m&#246;glich

COMMENT
-------
Schneeh&#246;he Rutschblock oben 2m, unten 3.20m Gel&#228;ndestufe</slf:text></slf:profiletext></slf:profiletext-list></caaml:customData></caaml:metaData><caaml:timeRef><caaml:recordTime><caaml:TimeInstant><caaml:timePosition>2013-02-26T11:45:00+01:00</caaml:timePosition></caaml:TimeInstant></caaml:recordTime><caaml:dateTimeReport>2013-02-27T10:36:51+01:00</caaml:dateTimeReport><caaml:dateTimeLastEdit>2013-02-27T11:38:06+01:00</caaml:dateTimeLastEdit></caaml:timeRef><caaml:srcRef/><caaml:locRef><caaml:name>Sirtenstockgr&#228;tli</caaml:name><caaml:validElevation><caaml:ElevationPosition uom="m"><caaml:position>2162</caaml:position></caaml:ElevationPosition></caaml:validElevation><caaml:validAspect><caaml:AspectPosition><caaml:position>NE</caaml:position></caaml:AspectPosition></caaml:validAspect><caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:SlopeAnglePosition uom="deg"><caaml:position>45</caaml:position></caaml:SlopeAnglePosition></caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:pointLocation><gml:Point id="pointID" srsName="urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84" srsDimension="2"><gml:pos>8.748402 46.895488</gml:pos></gml:Point></caaml:pointLocation></caaml:locRef><caaml:snowProfileResultsOf><caaml:SnowProfileMeasurements dir="top down"><caaml:profileDepth uom="cm">200.0</caaml:profileDepth><caaml:weatherCond><caaml:airTempPres uom="degC">-5.7</caaml:airTempPres></caaml:weatherCond><caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:hS><caaml:Components><caaml:height uom="cm">200.0</caaml:height></caaml:Components></caaml:hS></caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:stratProfile><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">0.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">37.0</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>DF</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainFormSecondary>RG</caaml:grainFormSecondary><caaml:grainSize uom="mm"><caaml:Components><caaml:avg>0.25</caaml:avg><caaml:avgMax>0.5</caaml:avgMax></caaml:Components></caaml:grainSize><caaml:hardness uom="">F</caaml:hardness></caaml:Layer><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop u